  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is a prospective, non-interventional, multi-center study. The primary objective of this
      study is to evaluate the image quality of Ultravist in patients requiring contrast-enhanced
      CT considering the routine use in patient population's, region's indication.
    </textblock>
